      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"6. MEPUNGA BREEZE last start finished 3rd over 730m at this track beaten 4.5 lengths (43.43) behind Amron Toy in a Grade 4/5 on April 11. Looks suited and should go close. 4. BAFFERT turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (37.87) last time in a Special conditions race at Shepparton. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Cannot be underestimated. 5. IN BLOOM has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fifth (43.53) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Expected to do much better this time. 1. PAW GRADY can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.\",\"runners\":[6,4,5,1],\"exclusive\":false}",
